column1: Poll options for How well do you know API testing and using an API testing tool such as postman
Beginner (I'm not even sure I know what a API is, the only postman I know is Pat)
Basic level (Very basic understanding of API testing once the tool is set up for me)
Intermediate level (I often do API testing and have experience using postman and setting up new requests)
Expert level (API testing is my life)
